{"type": "article", "id": 14818, "title": "日本出现了一个梦幻厕所，却暗示着一个黑暗预言", "description": "又是一个异（sang）想（xin）天（bing）开（kuang）的厕所设计案例。", "date": "2015-09-12T08:08:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6510, "name": "厕所"}, {"id": 50, "name": "日本"}, {"id": 15926, "name": "厕所艺术节"}, {"id": 15927, "name": "Oita Toilennale"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 112, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021052227wW0zsUQKHfgXVpC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t最近，<a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2015/09/10/melting-dream-toilennale-minako-nishiyama/\" target=\"_blank\">日本街头出现了一个萌萌的厕所</a>。远远望去，它像是一个糖果店或是旋转木马，可是当你走近看，就会看见厕所的标志。它是由三位日本女性艺术家设计的，糖果概念由 Minako Nishiyama 提出，她与 Mika Kasahara 和 Yuma Haruna 一道合作，完成了这件作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105218FeOGwqCmDhfR6taZ.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\"糖果厕所的外观\" alt=\"糖果厕所的外观\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>糖果厕所的外观</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这三位艺术家将厕所起名为 <a href=\"http://meltingdream.pupu.jp\" target=\"_blank\">“Melting Dream”，</a>除了模仿糖果店的外形以外，当你走进厕所内部，就会看见厕所墙上快要融化的草莓冰淇淋装饰。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105219CMKkWBblGUmiTEFw.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\"厕所墙上的甜品图\" alt=\"厕所墙上的甜品图\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>厕所墙上的甜品图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105219FUqB1jnpaKWHJ0rG.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"490\" title=\"猛地一看，像是一些“鲜肉”\" alt=\"猛地一看，像是一些“鲜肉”\" data-ratio=\"0.765625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>猛地一看，半融化的冰淇淋像是一些“鲜肉”，带有些许色情的意味</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105220vjTeL1MBhZ4fHOy3.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" title=\"厕所门\" alt=\"厕所门\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>厕所门</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>除了稍带有色情意味之外，设计师们给它赋予了更多内涵。她们在厕所中加入了一些黑色预言，在接受媒体采访时，她们说，“这些即将融化的冰淇淋代表着日本。日本是个暧昧不清的国度，它正在一点点瓦解。</span><span>” 她说厕所的设计灵感源于 4 年前的福岛核电站泄露事故。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105220R5Nn8kiQySBLCElt.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"491\" title=\"洗手池\" alt=\"洗手池\" data-ratio=\"0.7671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>洗手池</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105221Ro01leKvIHsgMSmN.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"492\" title=\"外部的细节\" alt=\"外部的细节\" data-ratio=\"0.76875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>外部的细节</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105221O8vu0sUd6LM7ekW3.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"422\" title=\"洗手池及镜子旁的装饰\" alt=\"洗手池及镜子旁的装饰\" data-ratio=\"0.659375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>洗手池及镜子旁的装饰</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这件作品是 <a href=\"http://toilennale.jp/\">Oita Toilennale</a> 艺术节的一部分，这是世界上第一个以厕所为主题的艺术节，今年的活动已<a href=\"http://hyperallergic.com/232913/japan-wipes-away-pretentiousness-with-art-festival-devoted-to-toilets/\" target=\"_blank\">从今年 7 月份开始，将持续到 9 月 23 号。</a>在当地政府的邀请下，共有 16 件厕所装置亮相。主办者 Eisuke Sato 说艺术节的主要目的是促进当地旅游业的发展，以下是艺术节上出现过的一些作品：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105221xOHz6UiCErAkqge3.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\"Hiroshi Fuji, “UTTM~UsedToysToiletMuseum–” (2013)\" alt=\"Hiroshi Fuji, “UTTM~UsedToysToiletMuseum–” (2013)\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Hiroshi Fuji, “UTTM~UsedToysToiletMuseum–” (2013)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105222NwLYxK6e0SRrPy2s.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"782\" title=\"Yujiro Miyazaki, “Traveling Toilet” (2015)\" alt=\"Yujiro Miyazaki, “Traveling Toilet” (2015)\" data-ratio=\"1.221875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Yujiro Miyazaki, “Traveling Toilet” (2015)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105222PG9iXRo7DFY20Tcs.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"427\" title=\"Hiroyuki Matsukage, “Have no idea how to flush” (2015)\" alt=\"Hiroyuki Matsukage, “Have no idea how to flush” (2015)\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Hiroyuki Matsukage, “Have no idea how to flush” (2015)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.spoon-tamago.com/2015/09/10/melting-dream-toilennale-minako-nishiyama/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>spoon-tamago</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}